{"tid":839781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【佐敦之虎案】卧底警不可信9被告全脫罪 警放棄向餘下過百名疑犯提控","createTime":"2018-09-28T07:51:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-28T09:46:18.000Z","uid":20419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d5dfb36f3656c652373f5494a1fc5fdb07dd8122","tid":839781,"uid":20419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T07:51:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180928&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=58732872\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180928%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D58732872&d=B4nGfHi%2BlHStSkvHnZa08%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=2c77c62f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180928%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D58732872&h=d80b8fe6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180928&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=58732872</a> <br />\n【佐敦之虎案】卧底警不可信9被告全脫罪 警放棄向餘下過百名疑犯提控"},{"pid":"e33a77182c5d0557942d4b0a64befd6c2a53c510","tid":839781,"uid":20419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T07:52:29.000Z","msg":"警方前年執行代號「翡翠刀」的卧底行動，卧底探員滲入黑幫超過1年收集情報，期間結識「佐敦之虎」陳家建和多名「和勝和」成員。「佐敦之虎」涉自言獲「上海仔」支持將接任新坐館，又涉「吹雞」召集近百名手下與仇家談判，他與另外8人被控共24項罪名，案件經審訊後，法官今指卧底警證供不可信，不合理之處比比皆是，控方除依賴其口供無其他佐證，故裁定全部被告全部罪名不成立。據了解，整個「翡翠刀」行動共拘捕逾百人，但律政司將不會向其餘被捕人士提控。<br />\n<br />\n中第二及第九被告申請訟費獲批，各被告聞悉脫罪後均笑逐顏開，有人與律師及親友握手。首被告「佐敦之虎」陳家建亦連忙打電話報喜，包括向電話另一端表示「多謝阿頭」。早前稱病曾缺席及需戴口罩應訊的他，今早鼻子泛紅，向記者表示已康復。被問昨晚有否去飲喜宴，他回應「你話阿Me嗰度？冇去啦，風頭火勢。」<br />\n<br />\n佐敦之虎:曾勸卧底警「唔好吸咁多（毒品）」<br />\n<br />\n陳透露，自己和同門兄弟曾勸卧底警「唔好吸咁多（毒品）」，顯示卧底毒癮不淺，但陳也指可能是卧底扮出來的。被問卧底演技是否高超，陳笑着承認當初真的不知道他是卧底，「如果唔係我都唔會企喺法庭啦」，但他認為法律是公正的。有記者問裁決算不算還他一個公道，陳想了一想回答：「都可以咁講嘅。」"},{"pid":"b8e4c97c0ff1118a2f19bf875cf8187334be04fb","tid":839781,"uid":37528,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T07:53:37.000Z","msg":"成個行動涉及幾多錢？俾曬d餓底探員飲飲食食，叫雞揼骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8660a887912a1f44c70227a5a1ceed8548f8cc84","tid":839781,"uid":9193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T07:59:59.000Z","msg":"成個行動分分鐘洗左幾千萬 而家得個吉 <br />\n唔使講已經知冇人要負責"},{"pid":"fcb1f40b0a208beb764694bfd0922a4dda84fce8","tid":839781,"uid":164913,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T08:01:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9d41779759b60cfd757402d575f93b00ee20ceeb","tid":839781,"uid":3241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T08:02:23.000Z","msg":"好啦 浪費咁多警力而家講告唔入 <br />\n條25警出黎切腹啦 不過佢仲敢唔敢出九龍去信和行街街， 成百幾人想問候佢"},{"pid":"cee4b8dcefb2a108d252284eb9020cff8929c64b","tid":839781,"uid":56428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T08:02:29.000Z","msg":"警黑合作 做樣"},{"pid":"1d91d35057f9e0cbfd23ba15f01e13865342640c","tid":839781,"uid":20419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T08:05:38.000Z","msg":"警方2015年執行代號「翡翠刀（Jade Cutter）」卧底行動，派探員滲入黑幫和勝和搜證。惟卧底警員被質疑在行動中結識多達40多名女子，當中絕大部份甚年輕。辯方更指卧底與其中一名與案有關女子Mena拍拖，Mena的名字出現在卧底的流水簿上，二人曾在酒吧做出親密男女才會做的行為。卧底庭上否認，聲稱兩人僅屬普通朋友。不過，本報找到女主角在社交網站的帖文，顯示卧底行動曝光後，女主角似仍對卧底念念不忘：<br />\n<br />\n「有一種愛明明是深愛，卻說不出來&hellip;&hellip;有一種愛明知無前路，心卻早已收不回來。」<br />\n<br />\n案中女主角姓馬，洋名Mena，其社交帳號目前暫停運作。Mena曾在帖文內稱卧底警員鄭皓瑋為「我條仔」，並提及二人拍拖，顯示二人關係非一般。庭上證供更披露，女方將卧底化名的「維」字，紋身紋在肩背，辯方因此質疑：「普通朋友會紋個名？」"},{"pid":"f4b99984f3e6157b99b0bf75e648bb2a46a9f877","tid":839781,"uid":20419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T08:06:14.000Z","msg":"臥底強調，他與Mena是普通朋友，不知她紋上「維」字，反而自己能隨時陪伴首被告「佐敦之虎」陳家建外出，覺得陳「對我有好感」。此言一出，惹來庭上眾被告失笑。<br />\n<br />\nMena在卧底行動曝光後多次在社交帳號貼文「追憶」卧底，曾上載卧底的照片，並寫下：<br />\n<br />\n「我的最愛，生日快樂。」<br />\n<br />\n「又一夜無眠，很想你，你過得好嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n不過，Mena聲稱對卧底的警察身份毫不知情，去年7月中更發佈數百字帖文，力數卧底的同門兄弟經常找他外出蒲夜總會，所知應該比她更多：<br />\n<br />\n「真係好X好笑，嗰時我知我條仔係臥底嚟架？我都係被通知架咋，嗰時拍拍下拖你老味成日打嚟搵佢夾佢落去，又捉佢去食飯去夜總會去呢度去嗰度，唔知仲以為同我爭仔咁款，仲同我講佢好乖唔媾女架，佢出嚟只係陪我幫我做嘢。」<br />\n<br />\n「我嗰時搵佢唔到或者佢出咗事，我都係問佢身邊啲兄弟先知佢做緊乜嘢，連叫佢入屯門做嘢、差啲連條命都無X埋呢單嘢，我都係分咗手後先喺其他人口中聽返嚟，我知嘅嘢真係有幾多吖。」<br />\n<br />\nMena又在帖文中控訴被人滋擾，要求她找出卧底的「痛腳」和罪證，但她坦言所知不多：<br />\n爆咗針就嚟煩我，又叫我爆佢啲嘢出嚟，用下腦都諗到啦，佢明知自己係差佬，會唔會白紙黑字send wts同我講佢做過啲乜嘢知法犯法嘅嘢吖，白癡到等爆針後畀人拎出嚟、推翻晒自己呢兩年所做嘅一切吖？」<br />\n<br />\n「佢食嘢邊個叫架？關事嗰啲唔爆佢？個個都搵唔到佢痛腳，就覺得我係一定搵到嘅？一定要我爆？我可以爆啲乜嘢？上庭作文吖！自說自話又乜嘢證據都無，個官睬你都有味啦，唔X出庭爆響口就搞X我？搞X死我都無用，唔知就係唔X知！幾廿歲人個腦仲生喺屎忽度，我真係X你老母。」<br />\n<br />\nMena的朋友留言安慰稱「別理他們」，Mena回應道：<br />\n<br />\n「你兩個知嘅仲多過我，我真係畀你哋大佬激X死，個腦生喺屎忽度。」<br />\n<br />\n【案件編號：DCCC808/17】"},{"pid":"8c9b12a787437a56bf344e601f76e54c851dfa1a","tid":839781,"uid":20419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T08:07:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180928/large/1538119135_4b1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180928%2Flarge%2F1538119135_4b1e.jpg&h=9ff299fd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cfbe8cfb00b99f1ae0a079b3bae4e01013590ae6","tid":839781,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcb1f40b0a208beb764694bfd0922a4dda84fce8","tid":839781,"uid":164913,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T08:01:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T08:08:13.000Z","msg":"我記得成龍最後係私了<br />\n嗰時成龍啲電影係好睇嘅"},{"pid":"5b1cb8203a5c53f31c0257d93c594f6efe98a68f","tid":839781,"uid":172248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcb1f40b0a208beb764694bfd0922a4dda84fce8","tid":839781,"uid":164913,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T08:01:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T08:08:36.000Z","msg":"朱滔!!!!"},{"pid":"ee1aa8cb748e483358fc45378b06d88d7694553c","tid":839781,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T08:09:06.000Z","msg":"無個釘得死，個臥底呢次死撚硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n實比人買起都似<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82cc03e586090dc1c6eeeb5640d8280aea074e95","tid":839781,"uid":164913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T08:09:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"398f412e75aa8f29c9aacb665ae7a0cb71ae8a5e","tid":839781,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T08:10:10.000Z","msg":"個臥底之後會點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"153297aa4500b9b85f238c793562b8be0390c7f8","tid":839781,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82cc03e586090dc1c6eeeb5640d8280aea074e95","tid":839781,"uid":164913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfbe8cfb00b99f1ae0a079b3bae4e01013590ae6","tid":839781,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcb1f40b0a208beb764694bfd0922a4dda84fce8","tid":839781,"uid":164913,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T08:01:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T08:08:13.000Z","msg":"我記得成龍最後係私了<br />\n嗰時成龍啲電影係好睇嘅"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T08:09:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T08:15:27.000Z","msg":"好似唔係喎<br />\n警察故事嘛"},{"pid":"138ab484c7ea821a3188b1735b0a809f77dfb530","tid":839781,"uid":90609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T08:23:57.000Z","msg":"唔知佢做唔做得返警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c01aa36794c12d2cbc906e6d8d58f4644d0b7f62","tid":839781,"uid":164913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T08:41:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1ea0750cc82e50dd281c1c0a39213e0f46eac0f3","tid":839781,"uid":164913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T08:44:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3bebefd380397c472f2c52d6a130d8c55d62eb08","tid":839781,"uid":204717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T09:24:26.000Z","msg":"mena咩樣"},{"pid":"2943e33ab77f008f81fb592c8fa39115f40ca96d","tid":839781,"uid":900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T09:43:45.000Z","msg":"阿Me果度係咪沙田Me<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33a3e4f4b28d36d4e604c551214ecd8876c80197","tid":839781,"uid":8105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2943e33ab77f008f81fb592c8fa39115f40ca96d","tid":839781,"uid":900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T09:43:45.000Z","msg":"阿Me果度係咪沙田Me<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T09:46:18.000Z","msg":"油麻they<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}